Working in Monggo DB

first install the application for Local 

1. https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community
2. create a data base for your needs.
3. create a file in vscode name for your backend data query 
 1- install express https://expressjs.com/en/starter/installing.html
 2- install monggose https://www.npmjs.com/package/mongoose

Mongoose is for Schema 
Express for Routing 

What is nodemon
nodemon is a development tool for Node.js that automatically restarts your server when you change any backend files.

